          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The modern academy is one of the oldest CISCE-affiliated schools in Kolkata.The sch may be small but it has got excellent management skills. Sharing my personal experience , I studied in a reputed icse sch of Kolkata in lake gardens for 13 yrs..then I switched to this sch for plus 2.I feel it was one of my best decision to join the sch. The teachers are student-friendly ..although few may be strict they are good. The respect the students.they give their best to keep the students in a lively environment.Secondly it is a budget sch with ac facility.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "The Modern Academy - Selimpur"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Aditi Ghosh"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-09-08",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I'm a 2015 graduate. I'm ecstatic beyond measure to say that I've no complaints as such in spite of the fact that certain facilities should've been better. I'm enraptured by the two senior years I've spent in this school. Right here I've found the best thing to happen in my life. The environment helped me to improve in certain aspects. During my time, there were some good teachers who gave the effort to attend to every student and were also determinants of creating interests in our subjects.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
